libpmemobj-cpp (1.7-1) experimental; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
  * Merge in Ubuntu changes:
    + Add Breaks/Replaces for ≤ Disco.
    + Set Architecture to amd64 only (Ubuntu can't cope with
      BD-Uninstallable).
    + Register with doc-base.
    + Set Section of the -doc package.
  * B-Dep on pmemobj 1.6 (runtime still works with 1.5).
  * During tests, pretend we're running on pmem, to avoid msync.
  * Cherry-pick an upstream fix for basic_string.
  * Give pmpong autopkgtest Dep: on fontconfig.

 -- Adam Borowski <kilobyte@angband.pl>  Fri, 28 Jun 2019 14:03:34 +0200

